================
ConnectomeViewer
================

The ConnectomeViewer for Multi-Modal, Multi-Level Network Visualization and Analysis

The ConnectomeViewer is a extensible, scriptable, pythonic software tool for visualization
and analysis in structural neuroimaging research on many spatial scales. Employing the
Connectome File Format, diverse data such as networks, surfaces, volumes, tracks and metadata
are handled and integrated. 

Copyright (C) 2009-2010, Ecole Polytechnique Fédérale de Lausanne (EPFL) and
Hospital Center and University of Lausanne (UNIL-CHUV), Switzerland

